_sText:
Quite a simple minigame map idea...

You carve a fort with breakable blocks after 60 seconds you collect guns from the gun machine to the right. and fight.

NOTE!!!
-----
Servers will require some form of no-block otherwise the teleporters bug.
-----

Feel free to decompile this map but please give me credit for my work

Thanks... and enjoy
